short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Print all elements with z-index sorted by that number.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Adds "z-index" pane to DevTools' Elements panel. It shows ranking of elements sorted by z-index value. This would help you to reduce z-index numbers.

Stop `z-index: 999999` !!
